snippet.title: The Legend of Spyro: Dawn of the Dragon Mobile Catacombs
snippet.description:
The mobile version of this game is very different to the main console game, like most mobile games. Eh, I'm not too good at these, but enjoy!

Now, if only I could get my hands on the classic Spyro mobile games.....
